Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是「今日」 我的大女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在十五岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是「明日」 我的小女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还只有九岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不吵醒妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只让闹钟响了一下就起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.70,0:00:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上今日都要出去送报纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的烟火大会真让人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在遥远的天国守望着这两个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.70,0:01:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一能够留给你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那小小的约定而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.25,0:03:40.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}浴衣和烟火和苹果糖的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快点准备早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 去年为止的烟火大会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直让明日忍着不去看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今年的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这是昨天买东西剩下的零钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了今天我可一个子儿一个子儿地存着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟姐姐在烟火大会的摊位上好好享受一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苹果糖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有果酱仙贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早饭做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有烟火大会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 烟火大会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我打扫好了能不能出去一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 难得的周六嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会你就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的邻居 你的邮箱塞满东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 当心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.60,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会你就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房东 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是明日小妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蔬菜店的老板大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要摆摊卖蔬菜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祭奠摊位上是肯定卖不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赚点小钱的苹果糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是苹果糖铺子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会跟姐姐来买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 到时候预备个特别大的给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒面店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打靶屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棉花糖店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.40,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我回来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 灯都不开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 明日 你的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在桥本洋服店买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以穿妈妈留下的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是明日却没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就想买给你当礼物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道 这是 用小猪里的积蓄买的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快试穿看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了明日买的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把积蓄擅自用掉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得明日会高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 钱的话再存不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啦 擅自用掉是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但机会这么难得 就穿着浴衣去看烟火啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么烟火大会 我才不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏我那么期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备在烟火大会上一起用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果酱仙贝店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切我都那么期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.80,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想一起吃大大的苹果糖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣还是退掉吧
