Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快去接明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好险 安全达到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在学校吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是在外头的话 找到避雨的地方就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌打雷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 明日也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我啊 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐现在就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落下来了 就在很近的地方落下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 好像听人说过雨伞也会遭落雷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.10,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那个时候明日好像不是很怕打雷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候因为怕打雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去接明日的途中差点没放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对明日来说 可能并不需要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 小明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身都湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是感冒了怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 这件浴衣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件浴衣吗 很喜欢是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟姐姐穿的那件一样的样式哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小今说无论如何都要这个样式的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连我家的仓库都去找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能一整天都在找的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？一整天都在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年都没办法让明日穿浴衣 心里觉得很过意不去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我 拼命寻找配套的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.53,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来姐姐一直期待着和我穿一样的浴衣去烟火大会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 阵雨很快就会停的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记带伞的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好为难啊 回家要晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来接我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雨好像停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你没撑伞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐明明害怕打雷却还硬要来接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么难得就撑伞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很难为情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却总是给姐姐添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小今总是想着小明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却说她是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样我却对姐姐说了笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哦 小明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道出了什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可这件浴衣是姐姐拼命为你找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿起来给她看 这样不就好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.90,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋 键屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}江户时代(1603~1867)在江户(现在的东京)的隅田川由上游的「玉屋」及下游的「键屋」\N这两家有名的烟火制造商比赛放烟火 日本夏天最具代表的习俗烟火大会就源于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年都跟明日一起看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人就没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为明日会来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.90,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特制苹果糖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜店的老板大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日非常期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说要跟姐姐一起吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是要给你当向导 摊头的位置都作过调查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个目录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是明日为了给我当向导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把积蓄擅自用掉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么烟火大会 我才不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特大苹果糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日期待着跟我一起逛夜市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.40,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我却没有体谅到她的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明跟妈妈约定要好好照顾明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.70,0:17:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快点到姐姐那里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟火要结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明～日！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿上了浴衣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 今年也一起看到烟火了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也看到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.90,0:19:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 这样不行 快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我也想工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.60,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 钱的事情你不要担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐会加倍努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 工作也会多起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别丢下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别像爸爸那样消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 说了姐姐是笨蛋 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你哪里也不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里也不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.20,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐哪里也不会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心自己还不够努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我留给你们的只是一个小小的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们却好好地守护着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.70,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将来有一天 当尚且稚嫩的你们遇到力所不能及的事时…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的约定能够守护你们俩之间的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这样祈祷着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个月也会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.50,0:23:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的大魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.30,0:23:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 房东不来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷姐妹物语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.60,0:23:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房东和西瓜和探病的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.50,0:23:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请观看
